{
  "title": "圆周率",
  "keywords": "数学,学习,圆周率",
  "description": "圆周率的概念",
  "author": "",
  "createtime": "",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "title",
      "content": "圆周率 (<span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span>)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "style": "float:left; margin: 0 10px 5px 0;",
      "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/pi-dia.svg\" alt=\"pi circle diameter\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "画一个 <b>直径</b> (通过圆心到边上两点间的线段) 为 <b>1</b>的圆"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "然后这个圆的<b style=\"color:#cb0\">周长</b> (图形一周的长度) 就是 <b style=\"color:#cb0\">3.14159265...</b>   <b style=\"color:#cb0\">圆周率</b> "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "<b style=\"color:#cb0\">圆周率</b> 一般用希腊字母  <span class=\"pi\" style=\"color:#cb0\">&#x3C0;</span>来表示"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "content": []
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "style": "float:right; margin: 0 0 5px 10px;",
      "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/pi.svg\" alt=\"circumference, diameter, radius\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "<span class=\"pi\" style=\"color:#cb0\">&#x3C0;</span>的定义是:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "center",
      "content": " <i class=\"larger\">圆的<b>周长</b> <br>\n\t和 <b>直径</b> <br>\n\t的比值.</i>"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "content": []
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "style": "float:left; margin: 0 10px 5px 0;",
      "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/pi-dia-simple.svg\" alt=\"pi circle diameter\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0; "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "为了更好的理解<span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span> 是什么 ... 我们来一起画画这个图."
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "content": []
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "来自己计算一下"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "画一个圆，或者找一个圆形的盘子."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "先量一下它的(<b>周长</b>):"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "class": "center",
      "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/pi-plate-circumference.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"156\" alt=\"plate circumference 82\">\n\t\t\t<br> 大概是<b>82 厘米</b>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "再量一下它的 (<b>直径</b>):"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "class": "center",
      "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/pi-plate-diameter.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"194\" alt=\"plate diameter\">\n\t\t\t<br>大概是 <b>26 厘米</b> "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "周长/直径"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "class": "center large",
      "content": "82 厘米 / 26 厘米 = 3.1538... "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "非常接近 <span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span>的值."
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "圆周率的用途"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "当我们知道圆的直径，我们可以使用 <span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span> 来计算圆的周长"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "class": "center larger",
      "content": "周长 = <span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span> &#xD7; 直径"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "class": "example",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "threeheading",
          "content": "例如: 我们围绕着一个直径是100米的圆形广场走了一圈, 那我们实际走了多远呢?"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "class": "center",
          "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/pi-circle-ex1.gif\" width=\"230\" height=\"111\" alt=\"pi circle 100m diameter\">"
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "class": "tbl",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "example",
              "class": "row",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "left",
                  "content": "<span class=\"center\">走过的距离</span>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "right",
                  "content": " = 周长 <br>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "example",
              "class": "row",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "left",
                  "content": "&#xA0;"
                },
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "right",
                  "content": "= <span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span> &#xD7; 100 米"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "example",
              "class": "row",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "left",
                  "content": "&#xA0;"
                },
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "right",
                  "content": " = 314.159... 米 "
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "example",
              "class": "row",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "left",
                  "content": "&#xA0;"
                },
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "right",
                  "content": "<span class=\"center\">= <b>314 米</b>   </span>"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "当我们知道周长的时候，我们也可以使用 <span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span> 来计算直径."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "class": "center larger",
      "content": " 直径 = 周长 / <span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "class": "example",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "<img style=\"float:right; margin: 10px;\" src=\"../public/images/annulus-pipe.jpg\" width=\"118\" height=\"184\" alt=\"annulus pipe\">"
        },
        {
          "type": "threeheading",
          "content": "例如: 这根金属圆管的周长是94 毫米 ... 让我们来看看它的直径是多少?"
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "class": "tbl",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "example",
              "class": "row",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "left",
                  "content": "直径"
                },
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "right",
                  "content": " = 周长  / <span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span><br>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "example",
              "class": "row",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "left",
                  "content": "&#xA0;"
                },
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "right",
                  "content": "= 94 毫米 / <span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "example",
              "class": "row",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "left",
                  "content": "&#xA0;"
                },
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "right",
                  "content": " = 29.92... 毫米 "
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "example",
              "class": "row",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "left",
                  "content": "&#xA0;"
                },
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "class": "right",
                  "content": "<span class=\"center\">= <b>30 毫米</b> (我们取了一个近似值) </span>"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "半径"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "顾名思义，半径是直径的一半, 所以我们经常说:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "style": "float:left; margin: 0 20px 5px 0;",
      "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/pi-circle.gif\" width=\"172\" height=\"188\" alt=\"circle radius=1, half circumference=pi\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "对于一个 <b>半径</b> 是 <b>1</b>的圆"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": " 那么它的<i>周长的一半</i> 就是 <b><span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span> = 3.14159265...</b>"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "content": []
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "常数"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "<span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span>  约等于: "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "center",
      "class": "larger",
      "content": "<b>3.14159265358979323846&#x2026;</b>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "它是一个无理数，即无限不循环小数."
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "content": []
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "近似值"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "对于 <span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span>来说一个比较接近的值是   22/7"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "center",
      "class": "larger",
      "content": "22/7 = <b>3.1428571...</b>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "但这仅仅是一个近似值, 22/7 并不是完全<b>等于</b>. 事实上 <span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span> 不等于任何两个整数的比值, 它是一个 <a href=\"irrational-numbers.html\">无理数</a>."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "一个更加接近的比值是:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "class": "center",
      "content": "<span class=\"larger\">355/113 = <b>3.1415929...</b></span>\n\t\t\t<br>"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "常用值"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": " 我们最长用到的值是&quot;3.14159&quot;"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "前一百位"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "下面是<span class=\"pi\">&#x3C0;</span> 的前一百位的值:"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "border": "0",
      "align": "center",
      "content": [
        [
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "3.14159265358979323846264338327950288\n\t\t\t\t\t<br> 4197169399375105820974944592307816\n\t\t\t\t\t<br> 4062862089986280348253421170679..."
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    }
  ]
}